definition.value: Catalysis of the reaction -  3-beta-hydroxyandrost-5-en-17-one 3-sulfate + H2O -eq- 3-beta-hydroxyandrost-5-en-17-one + sulfate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  succinate + CoA + nucleotide triphosphate -eq- nucleotide diphosphate + phosphate + succinyl-CoA.
Catalysis of the reaction -  ATP + succinate + CoA -eq- ADP + succinyl-CoA + phosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  GTP + succinate + CoA -eq- GDP + succinyl-CoA + phosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  succinate semialdehyde + NAD+ + H2O -eq- succinate + NADH + H+.
Catalysis of the reaction -  H(2)O + succinyl-CoA -eq- CoA + H(+) + succinate.
Catalysis of the transfer of an adenylyl group from an adenosine nucleotide (ATP or ADP) to sulfate, forming adenylylsulfate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  ADP + H(+) + sulfate -eq- 5'-adenylyl sulfate + phosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  ATP + sulfate -eq- diphosphate + adenylylsulfate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  3-sulfino-L-alanine -eq- hypotaurine + CO2.
Catalysis of the reaction -  hydrogen sulfide + 3 NADP+ + 3 H2O -eq- sulfite + 3 NADPH + 3 H+.
Catalysis of the reaction -  2 superoxide + 2 H+ -eq- O2 + hydrogen peroxide.
Catalysis of the reaction -  TDP + H2O -eq- TMP + phosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  ATP + thiamine -eq- AMP + thiamine diphosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  4-amino-2-methyl-5-diphosphomethylpyrimidine + 4-methyl-5-(2-phosphoethyl)-thiazole + H(+) -eq- diphosphate + thiamine phosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  S-adenosyl-L-methionine(1+) + dimethyl sulfide -eq- S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + trimethylsulfonium.
Catalysis of the reaction -  NADP(+) + thioredoxin -eq- H(+) + NADPH + thioredoxin disulfide.
Catalysis of the reaction -  hydrogen cyanide + thiosulfate -eq- H(+) + sulfite + thiocyanate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  L-threonine -eq- glycine + acetaldehyde.
Catalysis of the reaction -  L-threonine -eq- 2-oxobutanoate + NH3.
Catalysis of the reaction -  O-phospho-L-homoserine + H2O -eq- L-threonine + phosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  prostaglandin H(2) -eq- thromboxane A(2).
Catalysis of the reaction -  ATP + thymidine -eq- ADP + thymidine 5'-phosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  ATP + thymidine 5'-phosphate -eq- ADP + thymidine 5'-diphosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  5,10-methylenetetrahydrofolate + dUMP -eq- 7,8-dihydrofolate + thymidylate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  3,5,3'-L-triiodo-L-thyronine + iodide + acceptor + H+ -eq- L-thyroxine + donor-H2.
Catalysis of the reaction -  sedoheptulose 7-phosphate + D-glyceraldehyde 3-phosphate -eq- D-erythrose 4-phosphate + D-fructose 6-phosphate.
Catalysis of the reversible transfer of a 2-carbon ketol group (CH2OH-CO-) from a ketose phosphate donor to an aldose phosphate acceptor.

Catalysis of the transposition of transposable elements or transposons. Transposases are involved in recombination required for transposition and are site-specific for the transposon|transposable element.
Catalysis of the reaction -  trehalose 6-phosphate + H2O -eq- trehalose + phosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  triacylglycerol + H2O -eq- diacylglycerol + a carboxylate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  D-glyceraldehyde 3-phosphate -eq- glycerone phosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  S-adenosyl-L-methionine + tRNA containing 5-aminomethyl-2-thiouridine -eq- S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + tRNA containing 5-methylaminomethyl-2-thiouridylate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  S-adenosyl-L-methionine + tRNA containing guanine -eq- S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + tRNA containing N2-methylguanine.
Catalysis of the reaction -  ATP + tRNA(n) -eq- diphosphate + tRNA(n+1).
Catalysis of the formation of aminoacyl-tRNA from ATP, amino acid, and tRNA with the release of diphosphate and AMP.
Catalysis of the reaction -  ATP + L-alanine + tRNA(Ala) -eq- AMP + diphosphate + L-alanyl-tRNA(Ala).
Catalysis of the reaction -  ATP + L-arginine + tRNA(Arg) -eq- AMP + diphosphate + L-arginyl-tRNA(Arg).
Catalysis of the reaction -  ATP + L-aspartate + tRNA(Asp) -eq- AMP + diphosphate + L-aspartyl-tRNA(Asp).
Catalysis of the reaction -  L-asparagine + ATP + tRNA(Asn) -eq- AMP + Asn-tRNA(Asn) + diphosphate + 2 H(+).
Catalysis of the reaction -  ATP + L-cysteine + tRNA(Cys) -eq- AMP + diphosphate + L-cysteinyl-tRNA(Cys).
Catalysis of the reaction -  ATP + L-glutamate + tRNA(Glu) -eq- AMP + diphosphate + L-glutamyl-tRNA(Glu).
Catalysis of the reaction -  ATP + L-glutamine + tRNA(Gln) -eq- AMP + diphosphate + L-glutaminyl-tRNA(Gln).
Catalysis of the reaction -  ATP + glycine + tRNA(Gly) -eq- AMP + diphosphate + glycyl-tRNA(Gly).
Catalysis of the reaction -  ATP + L-histidine + tRNA(His) -eq- AMP + diphosphate + L-histidyl-tRNA(His).
Catalysis of the reaction -  L-isoleucine + ATP + tRNA(Ile) -eq- L-isoleucyl-tRNA(Ile) + AMP + diphosphate + 2 H(+).
Catalysis of the reaction -  L-leucine + ATP + tRNA(Leu) -eq- AMP + diphosphate + 2 H(+) + Leu-tRNA(Leu).
Catalysis of the reaction -  ATP + L-lysine + tRNA(Lys) -eq- AMP + diphosphate + L-lysyl-tRNA(Lys).
Catalysis of the reaction -  ATP + L-methionine + tRNA(Met) -eq- AMP + diphosphate + L-methionyl-tRNA(Met).
Catalysis of the reaction -  ATP + L-phenylalanine + tRNA(Phe) -eq- AMP + diphosphate + L-phenylalanyl-tRNA(Phe).
